---
title: Glazed Beef Meatballs with Loaded Potato Wedges and Side Salad
description: Get a load of this meal! BBQ sauce-slathered beef meatballs and loaded potato wedges come together for a delightful explosion of flavours. Grab some napkins and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-boeuf-glacees-e5bd04a6.jpg
